text: Josef Jech (4 October 1886Other sources:1879 -ÖFB profile, 1880-transfermarkt – 19 November 1957) was an Austrian footballer. He played in two matches for the Austria national football team in 1908. ==International== In 1908 he played two matches for Austria. His first match was on 8 June 1908 versus England. His last match was on 1 November versus Hungary.
